## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all factors influencing cognitive development in middle childhood. Additionally, the lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the currency of the information. Further research, including longitudinal studies, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these developmental factors.